oracle.pgx.api.filter

Interface ResultSetFilter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResultSetEdgeFilter, ResultSetVertexFilter

    public interface ResultSetFilter
    Represents a filter interface used to create a vertex/edge set out of the PGQL result set.
